      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $E =  K^3$, $F = \\{ \\vec X = (x,y,z) \\text{ tq }  x + 2y + z = 0 \\}$\net $G = \\text{vect}\\bigl(\\vec U = (1,1,1)\\bigr)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E =  K^3\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F = \\{ \\vec X = (x,y,z) \\text{ tq }  x + 2y + z = 0 \\}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(G = \\text{vect}\\bigl(\\vec U = (1,1,1)\\bigr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f294cfe6-f68a-4088-9b98-b7e6464513d9",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Vérifier que $F \\oplus G = E$.",
        "html": "<p>Vérifier que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F \\oplus G = E\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3d0256e2-ca16-46af-9823-0affd803942b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $s$ la symétrie de base $F$ de direction $G$ et $\\vec X = (x,y,z)$.\n    Déterminer $s(\\vec X)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(s\\)</span> la symétrie de base <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F\\)</span> de direction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(G\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec X = (x,y,z)\\)</span>. Déterminer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(s(\\vec X)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "84fd3c99-8f5a-4609-a41d-46d32366228e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\begin{cases} 2x' = x - 2y - z  \\cr\n                  2y' = -x -z       \\cr\n                  2z' = -x -2y + z. \\cr \\end{cases}$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\begin{cases} 2x&#39; = x - 2y - z  \\cr\n                  2y&#39; = -x -z       \\cr\n                  2z&#39; = -x -2y + z. \\cr \\end{cases}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
